  <brief_title>Breast Augmentation Rehabilitation Program</brief_title>
  <official_title>How Rehabilitation Affects the Time to Pain-free Living After Endoscopic Transaxillary Subpectoral Breast Augmentation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
